OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly low cloud, mist and fog
OL,6,Flikely slowly clearing to leave a dry,
OL,7,Fmild and generally bright afternoon.
OL,8,FCloud thickening into the evening
OL,9,Fhowever, bringing some outbreaks of
OL,10,Frain for the north and west to end the
OL,11,Fday.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRain spreading east to all
OL,14,Fareas through Thursday evening,
OL,15,Fbecoming persistent overnight into
OL,16,FFriday. Turning cooler with an
OL,17,Fincreasing risk of sleet or snow over
OL,18,Fhigher ground of the Pennines.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
