OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FRain gradually easing into
OL,6,FFriday with cloud eventually breaking
OL,7,Fto perhaps giving some late
OL,8,Fbrightness. Feeling much cooler by day
OL,9,Funder widespread cloud, and a colder
OL,10,Fnight into Saturday.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,13,Fdrier and brighter day likely Saturday
OL,14,Fafter a cool start. Conditions
OL,15,Fbecoming cloudier and milder into
OL,16,FSunday and Monday, with low cloud, fog
OL,17,Fand some rain returning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
